name: Do I Have Everything?
description:
Woah! I've been invited on my very first multi-day hiking trip! ~YAY!~ But WHAT DO I PACK?!?!?! HELP before time runs out and I have to walk out the door and leave for my trip. I've got a list to help remind myself what I need, lets hope I don't forget anything...

This is a student Game created  with the intention to replicate a feeling and the way I feel packing for trips.
